Looking forward to seeing Tori's team take it home for #009mit tonight! 2.009 is a product development class for senior mechanical engineering majors, in which teams within the class develop and build products. The final team products are presented and marketed at tonight's event in front of reps and investors from companies around the world, faculty, students, and (in Tori's case) their softball coaches.
